<div class="title">Mind-blowing First Time</div>
<div class="substance">5-MeO-DMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Bob+Dobolina&Exact=1">Bob Dobolina</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Bob Dobolina. "Mind-blowing First Time: An Experience with 5-MeO-DMT (exp28671)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Nov 25, 2003. erowid.org/exp/28671</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

